00:19.207 --> 00:19.247
T{*\frz359.99}O{*\frz359.98}K{*\frz359.97}Y{*\frz359.95}O{*\frz359.94}, {*\frz359.92}N{*\frz359.91}E{*\frz359.89}R{*\frz359.88}I{*\frz359.87}M{*\frz359.86}A {*\frz359.84}W{*\frz359.82}A{*\frz359.81}RD

00:19.257 --> 00:21.797
<b>The details are still not cl—</b>

00:21.797 --> 00:21.967
<b>The details are still not cl—</b>

00:22.257 --> 00:23.757
<b>Vexing thing.</b>

00:47.537 --> 00:48.607
<b>You lowlife!</b>

00:48.607 --> 00:49.887
<b>Hand over that apple at once!</b>

00:49.887 --> 00:50.917
<b>Let me have it!</b>

00:50.917 --> 00:52.177
<b>No!</b>

00:52.177 --> 00:53.417
<b>They're all mine!</b>

00:53.417 --> 00:56.417
<b>I'm not giving any apples
 to someone who ran from the enemy!</b>

00:56.417 --> 00:57.877
<b>I did not run!</b>

00:57.877 --> 01:00.167
<b>I was merely hungry, and thus left for a meal!{TLC, minor: she doesn't really say she went for a meal, the word she uses here is she "went home", but I'm okay personally okay with this line. noting here if you care about being more accurate.}</b>

01:00.167 --> 01:01.177
<b>Yeah, right!</b>

01:01.177 --> 01:02.157
<b>Coward! Chicken!</b>

01:02.157 --> 01:03.927
<b>You are the one lying!</b>

01:03.927 --> 01:05.297
<b>You bitch!</b>

01:05.297 --> 01:06.647
<b>What did you say?!</b>

01:06.647 --> 01:07.807
<b>The Fourth Division...</b>

01:08.587 --> 01:09.807
<b>What?{both}</b>

01:10.737 --> 01:13.207
<b>Who's still alive from the Fourth Division?</b>

01:17.537 --> 01:19.417
<b>The tiny girl, Kobeni.</b>

01:19.417 --> 01:22.067
<b>And that four-eyed dude,</b>

01:22.067 --> 01:23.897
<b>but I heard he quit after that.</b>

01:30.737 --> 01:33.957
<b>Makima wants to see me and Pow, so we're leaving.{for the first time he uses a nickname for Power here - パワ子[Pawako] - is shortening to "Pow" good?}{sure, I like it}</b>

01:34.307 --> 01:37.417
<b>We just came to consume the fruits left for you.{absolute assholes lmao}</b>

01:44.747 --> 01:47.927
<b>I'm leaving an apple for you.</b>

01:47.927 --> 01:48.997
<b>Later.</b>

02:21.477 --> 02:24.957
<b>Curse, how long do I have left?</b>

02:29.067 --> 02:30.807
<b>Two years.</b>

03:41.697 --> 03:44.757
<b><i>I came to get a magazine I forgot, but he's crying.</i></b>

03:47.277 --> 03:49.547
<b><i>I guess that's understandable.</i></b>

03:49.547 --> 03:51.757
<b><i>A lot of his colleagues died.</i></b>

03:52.407 --> 03:54.957
<b><i>Including his partner, Himeno.</i></b>

03:56.337 --> 03:57.017
<b><i>Huh?</i></b>

03:58.667 --> 03:59.267
<b><i>Hold on.</i></b>

04:01.477 --> 04:02.467
<b><i>Huh?</i></b>

04:11.857 --> 04:15.327
<b><i>I was sad when Pochita died.</i></b>

04:18.037 --> 04:20.327
<b><i>But Himeno's death...</i></b>

04:21.337 --> 04:22.377
<b><i>Huh?</i></b>

04:23.237 --> 04:26.877
<b><i>She's the first person who wanted to be my friend.</i></b>

04:26.877 --> 04:28.307
<b><i>That's pretty cold of me.{tlc: In this line he's asking a question to himself, not making a statement. Disregard if this is fine in English.}</i></b>

04:29.457 --> 04:31.837
<b><i>Would I cry if Power died?</i></b>

04:33.077 --> 04:34.847
<b><i>Probably not.</i></b>

04:35.557 --> 04:39.597
<b><i>Not if he died either.</i></b>

04:42.167 --> 04:44.577
<b><i>What if Makima died?</i></b>

04:52.897 --> 04:57.627
<b><i>If she died, I'd probably be sad for a while.</i></b>

04:57.627 --> 05:00.717
<b><i>But I think I'd be back to enjoying life in a few days.{TLC, minor: He specifically mentions "three days" here but I'm okay with this personally, just marking it if you care about being accurate.}</i></b>

05:01.447 --> 05:07.067
<b><i>After all, getting three meals a day, some good sleep,
 and a bath is a dream come true for me.</i></b>

05:11.647 --> 05:16.387
<b><i>Did I lose my human emotions along with my human heart?</i></b>

05:21.167 --> 05:24.097
<b>Whatever! No need to think about serious stuff!{no thoughts, head empty}</b>

05:25.317 --> 05:28.717
<b>Thinking about things that aren't fun
 just makes your life unfun.</b>

05:28.717 --> 05:30.957
<b>Let's just go see Makima.</b>

05:30.957 --> 05:32.737
<b>How depressing...</b>

05:37.537 --> 05:38.847
<b>Excuse the intrusion.</b>

05:41.697 --> 05:42.417
<b>Hello.</b>

05:42.857 --> 05:45.407
<b>Oh? Were you crying?</b>

05:45.407 --> 05:47.437
<b>Should we come back in a bit?</b>

05:47.437 --> 05:48.747
<b>Who are you?</b>

05:49.967 --> 05:55.817
<b>Makima asked us to come over from Kyoto
 and coach the Fourth Division.</b>

05:55.817 --> 05:57.927
<b>Can I have that apple?</b>

06:00.477 --> 06:01.667
<b>Coaching?</b>

06:04.777 --> 06:06.967
<b>After the hotel incident and this attack,</b>

06:06.967 --> 06:10.937
<b>we know that enemy forces are targeting you, Denji.</b>

06:11.487 --> 06:14.697
<b>So I wanted to train up the Fourth Division...</b>

06:15.247 --> 06:17.177
<b>But most of its members died.</b>

06:17.177 --> 06:19.447
<b>Are you going to train us?</b>

06:20.027 --> 06:24.907
<b>Unfortunately, I'm going to be very busy
 with other things, but you'll be in good hands.</b>

06:26.167 --> 06:28.827
<b>This man will be coaching the two of you.</b>

06:40.277 --> 06:41.167
<b>His name is—</b>

06:41.167 --> 06:42.217
<b>Shh.{TLC: maybe "shh" instead?}</b>

06:44.057 --> 06:45.107
<b>You be quiet.</b>

06:46.047 --> 06:48.477
<b>Answer my questions.</b>

06:49.307 --> 06:51.727
<b>What was your reaction to your comrades dying?</b>

06:52.107 --> 06:53.057
<b>Whatever.</b>

06:53.057 --> 06:54.607
<b>I thought, "they're dead".</b>

06:55.127 --> 06:57.107
<b>Do you want revenge on the enemy?</b>

06:57.497 --> 06:59.827
<b>Revenge is gloomy stuff, and I don't like that.</b>

06:59.827 --> 07:00.737
<b>Same.</b>

07:01.317 --> 07:04.747
<b>Whose side are you on? The humans or the devils?</b>

07:07.317 --> 07:08.997
<b>Whoever will look after me.</b>

07:08.997 --> 07:10.377
<b>Whoever is winning.</b>

07:19.487 --> 07:20.927
<b>You two</b>

07:21.537 --> 07:23.177
<b>get full marks.</b>

07:23.657 --> 07:24.677
<b>What?{both}</b>

07:25.237 --> 07:28.247
<b>There aren't many people like you.</b>

07:28.247 --> 07:29.937
<b>You're wonderful.</b>

07:30.667 --> 07:32.437
<b>I love you.</b>

07:34.337 --> 07:35.317
<b>He's scary.</b>

07:35.637 --> 07:37.967
<b>Makima, you can go.</b>

07:37.967 --> 07:39.567
<b>I'll start their training right away.</b>

07:41.617 --> 07:42.987
<b>I'm leaving them in your hands.</b>

07:42.987 --> 07:43.777
<b>Makima?!</b>

07:45.697 --> 07:49.237
<b>I'm a devil hunter in the First Division.</b>

07:49.237 --> 07:53.577
<b>I like people calling me "teacher",
 so just go with that.</b>

07:54.727 --> 07:59.177
<b>I like booze, women, and killing devils.</b>

07:59.177 --> 08:00.177
<b>Huh?</b>

08:00.177 --> 08:01.177
<b>What?</b>

08:26.097 --> 08:28.047
<b>C-Cannot get up.</b>

08:30.777 --> 08:35.177
<b>You have the same muscles and bones as us.</b>

08:35.177 --> 08:37.957
<b>Break your necks and you can't move.</b>

08:38.727 --> 08:40.587
<b>What makes you different, though...</b>

08:40.587 --> 08:42.337
<b>The smell of blood!</b>

08:45.747 --> 08:48.417
<b>is that drinking blood heals you.</b>

08:51.697 --> 08:53.847
<b>Ugh, damn it!</b>

08:55.057 --> 08:57.377
<b>Are you messing with us?</b>

08:59.077 --> 09:02.557
<b>Makima asked me to train you up.</b>

09:03.917 --> 09:08.527
<b>For some reason, the Gun Devil wants your heart.</b>

09:08.527 --> 09:12.867
<b>So you being a wimp and getting
 taken out easily is a problem for us.</b>

09:13.367 --> 09:15.457
<b>And why did you just strangle us?!</b>

09:16.087 --> 09:18.707
<b>I've trained humans,</b>

09:19.167 --> 09:22.497
<b>but I've never trained devils like you.</b>

09:22.497 --> 09:25.467
<b>So I got drunk and thought about what to do.</b>

09:26.097 --> 09:27.467
<b>And after a while,</b>

09:27.777 --> 09:31.727
<b>my alcohol-drenched brain eventually came up with an idea.</b>

09:31.727 --> 09:34.707
<b>I'm the strongest devil hunter.</b>

09:34.707 --> 09:38.977
<b>So a devil that can take me down must be the strongest devil.</b>

09:39.517 --> 09:42.487
<b>So I'm going to hunt the two of you
 until you improve</b>

09:42.887 --> 09:45.987
<b>to the point where you can take me down.</b>

09:47.857 --> 09:50.047
<b>This man is a lunatic.</b>

09:50.047 --> 09:50.867
<b>Totally!</b>

09:53.487 --> 09:55.367
<b>Okay, let's continue.</b>

09:55.687 --> 09:59.127
<b>Remember that we'll get arrested
 if we end up killing a drunk old fart.</b>

09:59.607 --> 10:00.457
<b>Denji!</b>

10:38.717 --> 10:41.047
<b>The boy is immortal.</b>

10:41.357 --> 10:44.167
<b>The fiend is half-immortal.</b>

10:44.527 --> 10:48.797
<b>Both have the mindset to just
 take a hammer to a person's head right away.</b>

10:48.797 --> 10:51.427
<b>You don't have any humans rights.</b>

10:52.187 --> 10:56.767
<b>Even when I was a kid, I was so strong
 that I broke my toys right away.</b>

10:57.687 --> 11:01.187
<b>So I wanted toys that don't break.</b>

11:01.787 --> 11:06.947
<b>I'm going to make the two of you
 into a couple of serious badasses.</b>

11:13.577 --> 11:14.297
<b>Yip.</b>

11:20.957 --> 11:23.587
<b>See? It won't come.</b>

11:23.957 --> 11:27.047
<b>You used the Fox too rashly
 and it came to dislike you.</b>

11:27.047 --> 11:30.587
<b>It'll probably never allow you to use it again.</b>

11:31.067 --> 11:34.417
<b>And that sword. It's the Curse Devil's, right?</b>

11:34.417 --> 11:36.597
<b>How many more times can you use that?</b>

11:37.667 --> 11:39.977
<b>Is this what you meant by coaching?</b>

11:40.527 --> 11:42.477
<b>You're quick to pick up.</b>

11:42.477 --> 11:47.607
<b>We came to provide career consultations
 for the humans of the Special Divisions.</b>

11:47.937 --> 11:52.367
<b>It might be a bit too direct to say, but this incident
 makes for a good opportunity to quit.</b>

11:52.927 --> 11:56.867
<b>There's already one person
 from your division who went private.</b>

11:57.327 --> 12:01.877
<b>But if you're going to stay,
 you'll have to be prepared to do what's required.</b>

12:02.747 --> 12:03.747
<b>What's required?</b>

12:04.157 --> 12:06.127
<b>Yes, indeed.</b>

12:06.447 --> 12:09.997
<b>If you're not quitting, you'll need to make
 a contract with a stronger devil</b>

12:09.997 --> 12:13.007
<b>in order to be of use to the Special Divisions.</b>

12:13.627 --> 12:17.007
<b>So either you quit the Bureau
 and enjoy the rest of your life,</b>

12:17.007 --> 12:19.797
<b>or you stay and go through hell.</b>

12:22.087 --> 12:27.757
<b>The devils that killed my family
 and my partner are both still alive.</b>

12:29.737 --> 12:32.027
<b>How am I supposed to quit?</b>

12:35.477 --> 12:36.727
<b>Is that so?</b>

12:36.727 --> 12:38.037
<b>Alright then.</b>

12:39.537 --> 12:42.837
<b>Well, it's already late today, so we'll take our leave.</b>

12:42.837 --> 12:45.787
<b>We'll bring you the papers tomorrow.</b>

12:48.427 --> 12:51.507
<b>I see that our seniors in Kyoto were right.</b>

12:53.057 --> 12:56.677
<b>They told us to be careful,
 because everyone in the Special Divisions...</b>

12:57.217 --> 12:58.107
<b>is crazy.</b>

12:59.597 --> 13:03.007
<b>You should try to see yourself objectively
 every once in a while.</b>

13:06.717 --> 13:07.687
<b>Oh.</b>

13:08.267 --> 13:10.317
<b>There's a woman here who wants to visit you.</b>

13:11.317 --> 13:13.007
<b>He's all yours.</b>

13:41.127 --> 13:43.137
<b>I'm going home to sleep.</b>

13:43.797 --> 13:46.397
<b>I'll come fetch you tomorrow.</b>

14:15.927 --> 14:18.617
<b>Your head is malfunctioning again!</b>

14:18.617 --> 14:22.387
<b>Heal! Heal! Heal! Heal! Heal! Heal!</b>

14:23.037 --> 14:24.307
<b>Heal!</b>

14:32.857 --> 14:35.817
<b>How many times did I get killed today?</b>

14:37.017 --> 14:39.067
<b>Over twenty.</b>

14:39.597 --> 14:45.077
<b>I was out cold for most of those times, so I don't know the exact number.{power can count??}</b>

14:50.027 --> 14:52.537
<b>That old man is too strong.</b>

14:52.537 --> 14:56.797
<b>It's really no fun if I have to keep living like this.</b>

14:56.797 --> 14:59.407
<b>I worked hard so I could enjoy life.</b>

14:59.407 --> 15:02.097
<b>Working hard to live a nasty life is shit.</b>

15:02.527 --> 15:04.367
<b>How about we run away together?</b>

15:04.367 --> 15:07.207
<b>If we run, they'll treat it as us leaving the Bureau,</b>

15:07.207 --> 15:10.857
<b>and that means treating us 
like any other pair of devils.</b>

15:19.957 --> 15:22.617
<b>That damn drunkard!</b>

15:22.967 --> 15:26.397
<b>Treating us like we're his toys!</b>

15:26.397 --> 15:28.497
<b>I'm starting to get really pissed off.</b>

15:28.497 --> 15:29.747
<b>I got it!</b>

15:30.767 --> 15:31.647
<b>What?</b>

15:31.647 --> 15:34.057
<b>How to defeat him!</b>

15:34.057 --> 15:35.757
<b>He is <i>super</i> strong.</b>

15:36.107 --> 15:39.497
<b>However, the alcohol has destroyed his brain.</b>

15:39.497 --> 15:43.057
<b>We need to use our heads to fight him!</b>

15:43.057 --> 15:44.507
<b>Oh, yeah!</b>

15:44.927 --> 15:47.967
<b>I've been into that kind of stuff lately.</b>

15:47.967 --> 15:52.267
<b>Like how cool would it be to fight like the smart manga characters!</b>

15:52.267 --> 15:55.277
<b>We are going to kill him with our brains!</b>

15:55.827 --> 15:59.327
<b>I feel like I totally got smarter just now.{###needs TLC verification}{okay - cakey}</b>

15:59.327 --> 16:01.037
<b>You as well?</b>

16:01.037 --> 16:03.937
<b>I just came up with about a hundred plans.</b>

16:03.937 --> 16:08.907
<b>If we dominate too much tomorrow,
 we need to be careful not to kill him.{TLC pls, not sure how much I can make it out}{check CCs/official TL, but Denji is saying something like "With two smart heads together, wouldn't (not) doing XXX get harder?" and I personally cannot hear the rest over the loud music either.}</b>

16:08.907 --> 16:11.957
<b>He is going to be the toy next time.</b>

16:15.497 --> 16:18.427
<b>This should be their floor.{TLC: I am personally okay with this but for accuracy's sake he's actually saying "Their house should be (around here)...". Maybe add a "should" to keep the uncertain/guessing nuance}</b>

16:19.217 --> 16:21.457
<b>That smell of blood!</b>

16:21.457 --> 16:23.347
<b>He's here. That old drunkard.</b>

16:23.647 --> 16:26.437
<b>The man who wants
 to destroy our comfortable lives.</b>

16:26.437 --> 16:27.347
<b>Death to him.</b>

16:31.267 --> 16:34.477
<b>Now commencing Operation Super-Smart.{hot hot hot hot hot}</b>

16:48.157 --> 16:49.417
<b>Oh?</b>

16:49.417 --> 16:50.707
<b>A blood weapon.</b>

16:51.177 --> 16:53.707
<b>And she went for the head.</b>

16:54.427 --> 16:56.357
<b>Going for a cheeky ambush.</b>

16:56.357 --> 16:59.377
<b>They want to be the hunters this time.</b>

17:32.907 --> 17:34.957
<b>That... hurt.</b>

17:36.147 --> 17:39.047
<b>That was your best attempt so far.</b>

19:49.287 --> 19:51.297
<b>You're fighting better than last time.</b>

19:51.297 --> 19:56.677
<b>With my power, your right eye
 can see a little while into the future.{Clairvoyance C+}</b>

20:15.067 --> 20:17.117
<b>Up to you to use what you see, though.{TLC: mmm this works well and flows good but is somewhat bordering on a mistranslation. He's literally saying: "But that's all you can do" or "That's all my power does, though"}{assuming this is fine}</b>

20:36.927 --> 20:38.767
<b>Go ahead and strangle him to death.</b>

20:38.767 --> 20:41.767
<b></b>

